  "expedition": true,
  "objective": "Cross the burning island of the exiles — forge the Lythium Seal at the cold anvil, strike the rite amid the lava, toll seven of ten mourning bells before the furnace swallows them, and take the heading to Genesis",
  "time": 900,
  "weather": "ashstorm",
